        "dimensions": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "description": "    Enumeration of standardized dimensions used in online advertising projections.\r\n\r\n    Each member represents a dimension or attribute commonly used in digital marketing analytics,\r\n    campaign performance tracking, and audience segmentation.\r\n\r\n    Glossary:\r\n        Advertiser\r\n            Name or entity running the ad campaign(s). Also called Client\r\n\r\n        MarketingCampaign\r\n            Full name of the marketing campaign. A group of ad sets.\r\n\r\n        Campaign\r\n            An ad set.\r\n\r\n        MediaType\r\n            Type of media used (e.g., video, display, native).\r\n\r\n        MarketingCampaignGoal\r\n            Marketing campaign objective (Retention, Acquisition)\r\n\r\n        Category\r\n            Product or content category (e.g., electronics, fashion).\r\n\r\n        Device\r\n            Type of device used (e.g., mobile, desktop, tablet).\r\n\r\n        Os\r\n            Operating system of the device (e.g., iOS, Android, Windows).\r\n\r\n        AdChannel\r\n            Specific advertising channel (e.g., programmatic, direct).\r\n\r\n        AdSocialNetwork\r\n            Social media platform used (e.g., Facebook, TikTok).\r\n\r\n        Ad\r\n            A creative\r\n\r\n        Coupon\r\n            A creative coupon\r\n\r\n        AdFormat\r\n            Format of the ad (e.g., banner, interstitial, carousel).\r\n\r\n        DisplaySize\r\n            Size of the display area for the ad.\r\n\r\n        VideoPlacement\r\n            Placement type for video ads (e.g., in-stream, out-stream).\r\n\r\n        VideoPlaybackMethod\r\n            How the video was played (e.g., autoplay, click-to-play).\r\n\r\n        VideoPlayerSize\r\n            Dimensions of the video player.\r\n\r\n        VideoDurationInSeconds\r\n            Length of the video ad.\r\n\r\n        VideoPlayerRatio\r\n            Aspect ratio of the video player (e.g., 16:9).\r\n\r\n        Ssp\r\n            Supply Side Partner. The publishing network where displays were made.\r\n\r\n        Country\r\n            Country where the ad was served.\r\n\r\n        Region\r\n            Region or state within the country.\r\n\r\n        PostalCode\r\n            Postal or ZIP code.\r\n\r\n        UserBehavior\r\n            Behavioral segment of the user (e.g., frequent buyer).\r\n",
            "type": "string",
