        "metrics": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "description": "    Metrics represents the quantity that we wish to measure\r\n\r\n    Glossary:\r\n        Audience\r\n            Users or devices that were seen online and were eligible to be served an ad. When\r\n            several devices can be related to one user, it counts for 1, otherwise it reflects the\r\n            number of devices\r\n\r\n        Clicks\r\n            The number of clicks driven by the ads\r\n\r\n        Cost\r\n            The overall cost of your ads or video ads\r\n\r\n        CostPerResult\r\n            What your ad set has cost per configured result unit for your selected period.\r\n\r\n        Cpc\r\n            Cost Per Click - the amount of money spent for the ads to receive one click\r\n\r\n        Cpm\r\n            Cost Per Mille - the amount of money spent per thousand displays, available for CPM\r\n            based ad sets only\r\n\r\n        Ctr\r\n            Click-Through Rate - literally, the rate or frequency at which users click through to a\r\n            landing page from an ad\r\n\r\n        Displays\r\n            The number of times your ads have been shown on a screen\r\n\r\n        Ecpm\r\n            Effective Cost Per Mille - the amount of money spent per thousand displays\r\n\r\n        ExposedUsers\r\n            The number of users who have been served an ad\r\n\r\n        Frequency\r\n            The average number of displays each exposed user has seen.\r\n\r\n        InvalidClicks\r\n            Clicks that don\u0027t meet our quality standards and won\u0027t be billed to you.\r\n\r\n        InvalidDisplays\r\n            Displays that don\u0027t meet our quality standards and won\u0027t be billed to you.\r\n\r\n        Reach\r\n            Share of online eligible users or devices who have been served an ad\r\n\r\n        Result\r\n            What your ad set has achieved based on your configuration for your selected period.\r\n\r\n        UntrackableDisplays\r\n\r\n        NonViewableDisplays\r\n\r\n        Viewability\r\n            The percentage of displayed ads or videos ads that were considered viewable\r\n\r\n        ViewableDisplays\r\n            The number of times at least 50% of the ad appeared for at least 1 second for ads and 2\r\n            seconds for videos ads, once started\r\n\r\n        Visits\r\n            The number of users that were active on your site or app in the hour following clicking\r\n            on your ad\r\n\r\n        Winrate\r\n            Number of displays divided by the total number of display opportunities\r\n\r\n        BounceRate\r\n            Proportion of website visitors leaving after seeing only one page\r\n\r\n        Cpv\r\n            Cost Per Visit - the amount of money spent to get one visit on your website\r\n\r\n        AppInstall\r\n            The number of installations of application\r\n\r\n        Cpi\r\n            Cost Per Install - the amount of money that needs to be spent to get one app installed\r\n\r\n        Cpqv\r\n            Cost Per Qualified Visit - the amount of money spent to get one qualified visit on your\r\n            website\r\n\r\n        InstallRate\r\n            Install Rate - the percentage of completed app installs compared to the clicks that\r\n            occurred\r\n\r\n        QualifiedVisits\r\n            The number of users on the target website for which at least two events or one sale\r\n            event occurred within the hour following the click\r\n\r\n        Assists\r\n            The number of sales one of your campaigns or ad sets contributed to (with clicks or\r\n            displays) on your site or app.\r\n\r\n        AvgCart\r\n            Average revenue generated by a sale\r\n\r\n        Cos\r\n            Cost Of Sales - the ratio between the cost generated by the ad set(s) vs. the revenue\r\n            generated by the sales, figured as a percentage\r\n\r\n        Cpov\r\n            Cost Per Store Visit - the amount of money spent to get one visit on your physical store\r\n\r\n        Cov\r\n            Cost Of advertiser Value - the ratio between the advertiser value generated by the sales\r\n            vs. the cost generated by the ad set(s), figured as a percentage\r\n\r\n        Cpo\r\n            Cost Per Order - the amount of money that needs to be spent to get one order or\r\n            transaction\r\n\r\n        Cvr\r\n            ConVersion Rate - the percentage of completed purchases compared to the clicks that\r\n            occurred\r\n\r\n        AssistsSalesRatio\r\n            The ratio between your assisted sales and sales made on your site or app.\r\n\r\n        OmnichannelRevenue\r\n            The revenue generated by online and in-store sales.\r\n\r\n        OmnichannelRoas\r\n            Omnichannel Return on Ad Spend. The ratio between revenue generated online and in-store,\r\n            and the cost.\r\n\r\n        OmnichannelSales\r\n            The number of online and in store transactions or conversions resulting from Criteo ads.\r\n\r\n        Revenue\r\n            The amount of money generated by the online sales\r\n\r\n        Roas\r\n            Return On Ad Spend - the ratio between the revenue generated and the cost\r\n\r\n        Sales\r\n            The number of completed e-commerce transactions or purchases\r\n\r\n        OfflineRevenue\r\n            The amount of revenue generated by in-store sales.\r\n\r\n        OfflineRoas\r\n            Store Return on Ad Spend. The ratio between the revenue generated in-store and the cost.\r\n\r\n        OfflineSales\r\n            The number of completed in-store transactions or purchases.\r\n\r\n        OfflineVisits\r\n            The number of visits to one of the physical stores\r\n\r\n        Currency\r\n\r\n        VideoAvoc\r\n            The number of times one of your videos was viewable and audible when it reached\r\n            completion\r\n\r\n        VideoCompletionRate\r\n            The percentage of started videos that played for their entire duration\r\n\r\n        VideoCpcv\r\n            The average cost of a video played for its entire duration\r\n\r\n        VideoCpv\r\n            The average cost of a video that started playing\r\n\r\n        VideoComplete\r\n            The number of times one of your videos played for its entire duration\r\n\r\n        VideoFirstQuartile\r\n            The number of times one of your videos played to 25% of its duration\r\n\r\n        VideoMidpoint\r\n            The number of times one of your videos played to 50% of its duration\r\n\r\n        VideoThirdQuartile\r\n            The number of times one of your videos played to 75% of its duration\r\n\r\n        VideoAverageViewRate\r\n            The average played percentage of a started video\r\n\r\n        VideoStartRate\r\n            The percentage of displayed videos that started playing\r\n\r\n        VideoStart\r\n            The number of times one of your ads started playing",
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "Audience",
              "Clicks",
